{"tid":878553,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭一掌推開丈撓惠英紅索合照　安德尊成功攝位","createTime":"2018-10-27T08:34:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-30T02:58:23.000Z","uid":6497,"like":64,"dislike":72,"uniUserReply":73,"replies":[{"pid":"69a24a62e2bf2f61aa58ab8066a546c6a267db2d","tid":878553,"uid":6497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T08:34:12.000Z","msg":"前進啊gulliver boy<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181027/large/1540621807_ca7b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181027%2Flarge%2F1540621807_ca7b.jpg&h=b6fa7eb8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181027/58842166\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181027%2F58842166&d=GeleZsKVHoltJkiQ0jbYIywN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=5ab10083\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181027%2F58842166&h=28299d0d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181027/58842166</a><br />\n<br />\n【新增短片】<br />\n特首林鄭月娥在禮賓府舉行勳銜頒授典禮，共282人獲獎，其中武打影星惠英紅獲頒銅紫荊星章，惠有到場接受勳銜。林鄭亦趁機與惠撓手合照，「第一先生」林兆波原打算一同合照，但林鄭卻一掌推開丈夫，林兆波無奈退後。不過安德尊隨即「攝位」，成功與林鄭及惠英紅合照。"},{"pid":"f9b29c59459454545afc80c802570f96afee7ef4","tid":878553,"uid":38904,"like":198,"dislike":7,"score":191,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T08:42:57.000Z","msg":"馬英九睇手錶"},{"pid":"be41ce1fbd0b3c907e70e92da7b2bf41c99727f8","tid":878553,"uid":10757,"like":85,"dislike":1,"score":84,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T08:46:04.000Z","msg":"影完剩係同惠英紅傾計 安德尊做乜9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63359b5648cf03c223b6